On the flare up of the region .. A telephone call between Mohammed bin Salman and Macron
04 Nov 2019, 10:10 by مـــــــــــــــــــــــــس رضــــــــــا
Saudi Arabia's Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman has received a telephone call from French President Emmanuel Macron. It is noteworthy that the Saudi-French relations enjoy a strong and strong and a history of joint cooperation between the two countries throughout history and their keenness to coordinate positions on various issues. , And a solid friendship, between the two countries, is moving forward firmly and steadily. Pioneering and steady steps have been recorded in various fields, which are particularly important in light of the acceleration of international and regional changes, especially the political dimension;
